Fu Chuan just found out.

48
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,360
Does it matter?

49
00:03:53,470 --> 00:03:54,590
What's going on?

50
00:03:54,590 --> 00:03:55,640
Yes, he came back.

51
00:03:55,870 --> 00:03:56,990
But look at them.

52
00:03:57,150 --> 00:03:58,110
