that'd affect the races.

57
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:06,910
No.

58
00:04:06,910 --> 00:04:07,870
What did you say?

59
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:09,800
I mean,

60
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:11,640
