74
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:50,480
But I've never
had the courage to tell her.

75
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:54,680
I've watched her

76
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:57,720
train with another guy and get closer

77
00:04:58,510 --> 00:05:00,430
to him every day.

78
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,480
I've seen her jealous and upset

79
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:06,630
because of him.

80
00:05:07,390 --> 00:05:08,630
I've seen her in pain

81
00:05:08,630 --> 00:05:09,750
because of him.

82
00:05:14,630 --> 00:05:15,920
But there's nothing I can do.

83
00:05:20,270 --> 00:05:21,360
I can only stay by her side

84
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,430
as a friend.

85
00:05:25,270 --> 00:05:26,120
Do you mean Shen Yi?

86
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,080
Yes.

87
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,320
I like her.

88
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:32,950
I fell in love with her at first sight.

89
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,080
What's wrong?

90
00:05:44,390 --> 00:05:45,350
Are you scared

91
00:05:45,510 --> 00:05:46,630
I'll steal her from you?

92
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:48,510
Listen,

93
00:05:48,510 --> 00:05:49,950
if you keep pushing her away,

94
00:05:49,950 --> 00:05:50,910
you might lose her.

95
00:05:54,160 --> 00:05:55,120
Sometimes I really feel

96
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,240
you're so mean.

97
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:59,800
Didn't you know
she was a girl all along?

98
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:01,120
Why didn't you tell me?

99
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:02,520
What do you mean?

100
00:06:03,750 --> 00:06:04,800
You keep pushing her away

101
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,360
but don't allow others to like her, huh?

102
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:08,120
I've never pushed her away!

103
00:06:11,510 --> 00:06:14,120
At first, we ate, lived,
and slept together.

104
00:06:14,530 --> 00:06:16,240
I also had doubts about her gender.

105
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,990
But no one ever told me.

106
00:06:24,330 --> 00:06:26,760
I also hoped to feel
the same way about her

107
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,360
like I felt about

108
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,320
other teammates.

109
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:33,800
I don't know

110
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:37,680
when I fell in love with her.

111
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,280
I'm just confused.

112
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:49,870
Why did she

113
00:06:49,870 --> 00:06:50,870
refuse to tell me

114
00:06:50,870 --> 00:06:52,120
at the beginning?

115
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:56,390
Shen Yi, Shen Nan,

116
00:06:58,270 --> 00:06:59,720
