120
00:07:06,950 --> 00:07:08,120
No matter what she's called,

121
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,280
whether she has long or short hair,

122
00:07:10,390 --> 00:07:11,510
whether she's male or female,

123
00:07:11,510 --> 00:07:12,630
she's still herself.

124
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,120
Maybe you should ask yourself

125
00:07:20,630 --> 00:07:21,870
what you would be like

126
00:07:24,310 --> 00:07:25,390
