133
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:44,080
Actually...

134
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,630
Actually, I wanted
to tell you last time.

135
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,160
But...

136
00:08:51,150 --> 00:08:52,670
Later, I thought about it
for a long time.

137
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:55,160
Shen Yi,

138
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:57,840
I...

139
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,630
